# Flywheel README Compatibility Artifact

Canonical operator documentation lives in `README.md`.

This extensionless `README` exists because bead `flywheel-dw5w` AG3 named a
`README` artifact in its proof contract and the closed-bead audit correctly
flagged that path as missing.

## Validation Discipline

The validation-discipline operator workflow is documented in `README.md` under
the validation and callback sections. The paired doctrine lives in `AGENTS.md`
L71 `VALIDATE-AND-REDISPATCH-DISCIPLINE`; the cross-surface regression test is
`tests/doctrine-memory-wire.sh`.

Proof receipt for the audit-gap repair:

```text
B10_AG3=file:PASS path=README canonical=README.md
```

## Validation Command

```bash
bash tests/doctrine-memory-wire.sh
```
